pageContext.claim: “You know we've given -- I think it's 108 or 112 pages of financial detail to elections and you know, we have to file as the President, as any politician, you have to file. Nobody ever looks at that. When they do, they see how incredible the company is.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump's personal financial disclosure to the Federal Election Commission is detailed, but his tax returns would give a definitive and full account of how much he paid in taxes and the sources of his income.
